<br />

<br />
I just got done with my Eldrig camp.  I had been doing run by checks on Skyfire for months now, but decided to buckle down.   I convinced a group to stay at spawn spot, then ran to Graveyard and highsunned everything there.  One popped at camp.  They killed and left.  Anyway, four hours later, Eldrig spawned.  Timer was 26 minutes.  I would have wiped to him (was unbuffed) but a passing druid saved me.  
<br />

<br />
Went for UDB on Saturday, missed him by 10 minutes.  Anyway, keep up the hunt, you'll get him.  Last times I camped him I found his PH in the graveyard too.
<br />

